room_title: Escape room "Superheroes" by Escape Room Cleveland in Cleveland
room_description:
Your team of superheroes gets a call from the President about VEGA, a supercomputer originally created for maintaining energy consumption. It was later revealed that she is able to do a lot more: spy on top-secret government files or even launch a deadly space weapon!
The machine is not responding to orders and presents a threat. You have 60 minutes to disarm VEGA before it launches the space weapon and destroys the earth!
